Title: 数据流/状态流图
Describe: 消息、文件、部署配置和远端任务的状态所有权。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S07_DATA_OR_STATE_FLOW - agent 状态与工具数据流

[Description]
SDK 的核心状态包括消息、文件、记忆、skills metadata 和 async task tracking。状态扩展由中间件贡献，默认 `DeepAgentState` 只强制 messages 使用 DeltaChannel。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction
rectangle "User input" as Input
rectangle "DeepAgentState.messages" as Msg
rectangle "Middleware state extensions" as MWState
database "BackendProtocol" as Backend
rectangle "Tool outputs" as ToolOut
rectangle "Model response" as ModelOut

Input --> Msg : HumanMessage
Msg --> ModelOut : prompt context
ModelOut --> ToolOut : tool calls
ToolOut --> Backend : file reads writes execute
Backend --> MWState : files or task updates
ToolOut --> Msg : ToolMessage
MWState --> Msg : system prompt additions
Msg --> ModelOut : next turn
@enduml

[Detail]
`DeepAgentState` 在 `graph.py:63-66` 用 `DeltaChannel(_messages_delta_reducer, snapshot_frequency=50)` 控制 messages 历史合并成本。`FilesystemMiddleware` 的 `FilesystemState` 同样使用 DeltaChannel 管理 `files`，其 reducer 在 `libs/deepagents/deepagents/middleware/filesystem.py` 处理写入和删除。`AsyncSubAgentState` 在 `async_subagents.py` 用 `async_tasks` 记录 task id、agent name、thread id、run id 和 status。箭头表示数据流：用户消息进入 messages，模型产出工具调用，工具通过 backend 读写文件或执行命令，结果再回到 messages 或中间件状态。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S07_DATA_OR_STATE_FLOW - 部署项目数据流

[Description]
本地 managed-agent 项目的 `agent.json`、`AGENTS.md`、`tools.json`、`skills/` 和 `subagents/` 被解析为 `Project`，再转换为 API payload 与目录 commit delta。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction
folder "Project directory" as Dir
rectangle "Project.load" as Load
rectangle "Project dataclass" as Project
rectangle "build_payload" as Payload
rectangle "build_directory_files" as Files
rectangle "build_directory_delta" as Delta
cloud "Deep Agents API" as API
database "Local State" as State

Dir --> Load : agent.json AGENTS.md tools skills subagents
Load --> Project : validated data
Project --> Payload : metadata system prompt tools skills subagents
Project --> Files : managed file tree
Payload --> API : create or patch body
Files --> Delta : compare remote directory
Delta --> API : commit entries
API --> State : agent_id revision
@enduml

[Detail]
`Project.load` 在 `project.py:159-188` 返回纯 dataclass；`_read_agent_json` 在 `project.py:191-245` 校验 name、agent_id、model、runtime 和 backend。`build_payload`、`build_metadata_payload`、`build_directory_files`、`build_directory_delta` 分别位于 `payload.py:20-98`。目录同步只管理 `AGENTS.md`、`tools.json`、`skills/` 和 `subagents/` 路径，见 `_is_managed_path` 的 `payload.py:153-156`。这样可以把远端 metadata 与 Hub directory 文件状态分开维护。
